Privacy Policy
Introduction
This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and share your information when you use our File recovery & backup app. Please read this Privacy Policy carefully to understand how we handle your information.
Information We Collect
We collect the following types of information:
Personal Information: This may include your name, email address, phone number, and any other information that you choose to provide us.
Device Information: This may include your device type, operating system, and unique identifier.
Usage Information: This may include information about how you use the File recovery & backup app, such as the files you recover or backup, the frequency of use, and the date and time of use.
Log Data: This may include information such as your IP address, browser type, operating system, the time and date of your request, and referral URL.
How We Use Your Information
We use your information to:
Provide and improve the App
Send you important information about the App, such as updates and announcements
Personalize your experience
Respond to your inquiries and requests
Analyze how the App is used
Comply with legal obligations
Sharing Your Information
We may share your information with:
Third-party service providers who help us operate the App, such as cloud storage providers and data analytics providers
Law enforcement or other government agencies, if required by law or to protect our legal rights
Other third parties with your consent
Data Retention
We will retain your information for as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes described in this Privacy Policy unless a longer retention period is required or permitted by law.
Security
We take reasonable steps to protect your information from unauthorized access, use, disclosure, alteration, and destruction. However, no method of transmission over the Internet or electronic storage method is 100% secure. Therefore, we cannot guarantee the absolute security of your information.
User Choices and Controls
You have the following choices regarding your information:
You can access, correct, or delete your information by contacting us.
You can opt out of receiving marketing communications from us by following the instructions in the communications.
You can choose not to use the App.
Data Security
We take reasonable measures to protect your information from unauthorized access, use, disclosure, alteration, or destruction. However, no method of transmission over the Internet or method of electronic storage is 100% secure. Therefore, we cannot guarantee the absolute security of your information.
Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. If we make any material changes, we will notify you by email or by posting a notice on the App. Please review this Privacy Policy periodically for the latest information.
Contact Us
If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:
appifytechnology07@gmail.com
